<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-place-of">in place of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-in-sbs-sths-place">1.<strong>代替；取代 (in sb’s / sth’s place)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You can use yoghurt in place of cream to make this salad. 
你可以用酸奶替代奶油来做这道沙拉。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If I refused to go, they would send someone else in my place. 
如果我不去，他们会派其他人代替我的。</p></div></div>